column5: I saw this on FB today. Dave's new online TV Show gives him the forum to let loose a little. And he takes advantage of that!!  He even has a jar of...well...you watch cause you won't believe me.
AAAAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA! Need a "Not Safe for work" comment as all the people around my office kept walking by and asking me what I was laughing at...
Thats pretty great, I think we will make it a weekly feature!!
Thats a good idea!  These vids are really entertaining.
what a nut...take a breath every once in awhile HAHA
Dat boy is messed up y'all.
maybe its because he doesnt ever blink!
I would rather watch the "Sham Wow " guy !!!! Its like nails down a chalk board to me.
Chewing tinfoil also comes to mind..  Dave could do the slap chop too!!  Just razzing ya Dave..  Where'd you git that snazzy t-shirt tux??!
that was fricken funny great show again Dave.
He blinks at 3:07.  Inoticed that at first too... great video!
